{"description": "By default, the SELinux boolean <tt>secure_mode_insmod</tt> is disabled.\nThis setting should be configured to <sub idref=\"var_secure_mode_insmod\" />.\n<br/>\nTo set the <code>secure_mode_insmod</code> SELinux boolean, run the following command:\n<pre>$ sudo setsebool -P secure_mode_insmod <sub idref=\"var_secure_mode_insmod\" /></pre>", "rationale": "", "severity": "medium", "references": {"anssi": ["R48"]}, "control_references": {"anssi": ["R48"]}, "components": ["selinux"], "identifiers": {"cce": "CCE-84087-6"}, "ocil_clause": "secure_mode_insmod is not set as expected", "ocil": "\nRun the following command to get the current configured value for <code>secure_mode_insmod</code>\nSELinux boolean:\n<pre>$ getsebool secure_mode_insmod</pre>\nThe expected cofiguration is <sub idref=\"var_secure_mode_insmod\" />.\n\"on\" means true, and \"off\" means false", "oval_external_content": null, "fixtext": "", "checktext": "", "vuldiscussion": "", "srg_requirement": "", "warnings": [], "conflicts": [], "requires": [], "policy_specific_content": {}, "platform": null, "platforms": [], "sce_metadata": {"check-import": "stdout", "check-export": ["var_secure_mode_insmod=xccdf_org.ssgproject.content_value_var_secure_mode_insmod"], "platform": ["multi_platform_all"], "environment": "any", "filename": "sebool_secure_mode_insmod.sh", "relative_path": "rhel9/checks/sce/sebool_secure_mode_insmod.sh"}, "inherited_platforms": ["system_with_kernel", "selinux or bootc or osbuild"], "cpe_platform_names": [], "inherited_cpe_platform_names": ["bootc_or_osbuild_or_selinux", "system_with_kernel"], "bash_conditional": null, "fixes": {}, "check_type": null, "inputs": [], "expression": null, "failure_reason": null, "title": "Configure the secure_mode_insmod SELinux Boolean", "definition_location": "/home/greek_fire/.git/content/linux_os/guide/system/selinux/selinux-booleans/sebool_secure_mode_insmod/rule.yml", "template": {"name": "sebool", "vars": {"seboolid": "secure_mode_insm